<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>For Ayanda ❤️</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Great+Vibes&family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>

body{
    margin:0;
    font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:center;
    align-items:center;
    height:100vh;
    overflow:hidden;

    background: linear-gradient(-45deg,#ff9a9e,#fad0c4,#ffdde1,#ff758c);
    background-size:400% 400%;
    animation:gradientMove 12s ease infinite;
}

@keyframes gradientMove{
0%{background-position:0% 50%;}
50%{background-position:100% 50%;}
100%{background-position:0% 50%;}
}

/* intro screen */

#intro{
    position:absolute;
    color:white;
    font-size:40px;
    text-align:center;
    animation:fadeIn 3s ease;
}

@keyframes fadeIn{
from{opacity:0;}
to{opacity:1;}
}

/* main card */

.container{
    display:none;
    background:white;
    padding:50px;
    border-radius:20px;
    width:600px;
    text-align:center;
    box-shadow:0 15px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    z-index:10;
}

h1{
font-family:'Great Vibes',cursive;
font-size:60px;
color:#ff4d6d;
}

p{
font-size:18px;
line-height:1.7;
}

.song{
font-style:italic;
color:#666;
}

button{
margin-top:20px;
padding:12px 28px;
border:none;
border-radius:12px;
cursor:pointer;
font-family:'Poppins';
}

.yes{
background:#ff4d6d;
color:white;
}

.no{
background:#ddd;
}

/* hearts */

.heart{
position:fixed;
bottom:-10px;
font-size:22px;
animation:floatUp 6s linear infinite;
}

@keyframes floatUp{
0%{transform:translateY(0);opacity:1;}
100%{transform:translateY(-110vh);opacity:0;}
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<div id="intro">
A message for Ayanda ❤️
</div>

<!-- Floating hearts -->

<div class="heart" style="left:10%;animation-delay:0s;">❤️</div>
<div class="heart" style="left:25%;animation-delay:2s;">💖</div>
<div class="heart" style="left:40%;animation-delay:4s;">❤️</div>
<div class="heart" style="left:60%;animation-delay:1s;">💗</div>
<div class="heart" style="left:75%;animation-delay:3s;">❤️</div>
<div class="heart" style="left:90%;animation-delay:5s;">💖</div>

<div class="container" id="main">

<h1>Ayanda</h1>

<p>
I made this little page for you because I wanted to say something from the heart.
</p>

<p>
Remember the first time I saw you? I know I always tell you this story,
but I’ll forever cherish the day I first saw you because I knew right away
that's my forever girl.
</p>

<p>
I can't even fully describe what I felt in that moment.
It’s one of those once-in-a-lifetime feelings that you just know is real.
</p>

<p>
No matter what happens, that moment will always be special to me.
</p>

<p class="song">
Always & Forever – Mariah The Scientist 🎵
</p>

<p>
I’m not asking for anything big right now. Just a conversation.
</p>

<h2>Can we talk over FaceTime?</h2>

<button class="yes" onclick="alert('I’ll be waiting for your call ❤️')">Yes</button>
<button class="no" onclick="alert('I understand. Thank you for reading this.')">No</button>

</div>

<script>

setTimeout(function(){
document.getElementById("intro").style.display="none";
document.getElementById("main").style.display="block";
},4000);

</script>

</body>
</html>
